
The Graduate Student Community Service Committee (GSCSC) is a campus collection of UCD affiliates with the goal of encouraging graduate students to participate in the local community that was recently established by Human Corps and Professors for the Future.

The GSCSC mission statement is as follows:

  The Graduate Student Community Service Committee (GSCSC) is dedicated to encouraging graduate students to play an active role in their community through service. The committee provides opportunities for these students to contribute on many levels including providing service education and service projects for graduate students. The committee helps students find out about ongoing service opportunities and sponsors monthly service projects. 
